	* src/oniguruma/lonig.c: lonig.c: fix a mismatched type in two
	results of ?:; closes issue #1

2012-09-29  Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>

	* doc/manual.txt, src/algo.h, test/luatest.lua, test/onig_sets.lua,
	test/pcre_sets.lua, test/runtest.lua: Add the ability to use raw
	memory blocks as subjects.  The implementation is in algo.h, in the new check_subject function.  Usage is documented in manual.txt.  Optional tests have been added, using alien buffers.

2012-09-29  Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>

	* src/common.mak: common.mak: don't touch LUA_INIT, and augment,
	don't replace LUA_PATH

