2012-09-29  Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>

	* src/posix/lposix.c: lposix.c: simplify gmatch_pushsubject slightly

2012-09-29  Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>

	* src/posix/lposix.c: lposix.c: detect REG_STARTEND separately from
	other REX_POSIX_EXT features REG_STARTEND is implemented in some widely used libc's, e.g. GNU
	libc, which don't implement the other extensions.

